<<#If($FoundLinGinHueDisk=false)>>
    Thought: Guess I have to tell George Liao, then.
<<#EndIf>>

//接駁車停車場說明接駁車設定
//地窖含有微量輻射跟弱毒性氣體，補充說明閘門無法關閉就不要久待停車場(暗示設備不好)
//接駁車磁軌維修紀錄之類的，說明地窖地板有座懸凝處理，由車子去推地板移動

Nin Situ: And you, sir.;<< Play (司徒寧,MBU_司徒寧_醫院_側站看內)>>
Nin Situ: You should wait outside.
Thought: But Fran...;<< Play (戴士傑, MBU_戴士傑_便服3_側站抬頭) >>
Nin Situ: I know you're concerned about her condition.
Nin Situ: But we need space and privacy for some critical examinations.
Nin Situ: This can't be delayed. It's for her own good.
Nin Situ: There's a waiting area outside.;<< Play (司徒寧,MBU_司徒寧_醫院_側站看內返回)>>
Thought: I really don't want to leave Fran alone, but guess there's no other way...;<< Play (戴士傑, MBU_戴士傑_便服3_側站抬頭返回) >>
Thought: I'll wait outside, then.
<<#End>>
